{"tid":2505699,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮官員稱拜登將落實建議向富人開徵更高的資本利得稅","createTime":"2021-04-26T22:39:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T23:48:29.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"219cab1dc329c59fd536629cf95daa94e68d7c85","tid":2505699,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T22:39:52.000Z","msg":"白宮官員稱拜登將落實建議向富人開徵更高的資本利得稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587857-20210427.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587857-20210427.htm&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6%2F4XLRjZdTHGp6sdrEQ6olc%3D&h=1d1f12a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587857-20210427.htm&h=a3cfc4f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587857-20210427.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有白宮官員透露，總統拜登將落實建議對富人開徵更高的資本利得稅，協助國內進行基建投資，創造就業。<br />\n<br />\n白宮國家經濟委員會主任萊恩迪斯透露，買賣股票同其他資產獲利的徵稅增加，只會影響每年收入一百萬美元以上的人士，約有50萬人將要繳付增加後的富人稅。<br />\n<br />\n萊恩迪斯表示，新的稅款將會有助降低長期基建投資成本，同時改革美國稅階，令工作的人取得應有回報。他並沒有透露稅率，但<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">外界估計，因為投資而獲利的稅率會由現時20%大幅增加至39.6%。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n拜登即將會發表國情咨文。"},{"pid":"b0138a873739f8d64c080c5f37cc504c1567a51f","tid":2505699,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T23:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/car.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dba41dd3d44dc06a9e269c18805310adb68828e","tid":2505699,"uid":224882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T23:42:16.000Z","msg":"但係今日納指破左頂<br />\n大戶喜迎加税<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd79048a460f9df995240eb0d35937f5790639b4","tid":2505699,"uid":153408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi